1. *Uzrok* njegovog neuspjeha je neznanje.(The cause of his failure is ignorance.)
2. Ona se pokušavala sjetiti *uzroka* njihove svađe.(She tried to remember the cause of their argument.)
3. Da bismo razumjeli *uzroke* nastanka te bolesti, potrebno je detaljno istražiti.(In order to understand the causes of the emergence of this disease, it is necessary to research in detail.)
4. Glavni *uzrok* njegove smrti je bio prerani pubertet.(The main cause of his death was premature puberty.)
5. Ona se zalaže za sprečavanje *uzroka* zagađenja vazduha.(She advocates for preventing the causes of air pollution.)